Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一男人在山上方便被蜜蜂叮着命根子，晚上和老婆做完房事，老婆感慨说;结为夫妻三十年，只有今晚象过年，又长又大刚塞满，我爱蜜蜂一万年！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;5.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一穿裙美女，在井边打水，被一男子从身后插入强暴，警察问她当时为何不反抗？美女说;往前怕掉入井中，往后怕越插越深，往左往右给人家别断咋办！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;6.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;猪八戒与嫦俄正在广寒宫偷情，忽然窗外人影闪过，八戒急忙起身察看，嫦娥吃惊地问：何人？八戒答道：妈的，是杨利伟！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;7.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;父亲带儿子去洗澡，地很滑，儿子将要滑倒时一把抓住父亲的JJ才没有倒下，父亲骂到：他妈的！幸亏和我来的，要和你妈来非摔死你。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;8.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一农夫赶了头母猪给兽医配种，兽医瞧了说：看来这需要人工配种。农夫拽着手绕猪看了片刻，说：行是行，就是怕它咬我。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;9.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;是夜。夫于床上看书。不时将手伸入妻腿间。妻便脱衣撒娇。夫问：干吗？妻反问：你手干吗？夫一本正经的说：湿湿手。好翻书！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;10.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;老情人50年后见，亲热后老头叹：“ 一江春水干，两山成平川，只剩两颗葡萄干。”老太叹：“茅草堆里翻，不见枪和弹，一根萝卜干，还弯三道弯。”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;11.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男人有六个一样;平时象人一样，偷情象贼一样，约会象鬼一样，上床象狼一样，完事象猪一样，情人面前象猫一样，你不要笑！你也这样！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;12.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男知其与领导不轨，怒找领导妻，领导妻气急：“咱上床报复他俩。”事毕，领导妻说：“我还气，在报复一次。”一连五次，男跪倒趴下告饶：“求你了，我已经原谅他们了。”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;13.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;市长带两随从去爬山，不慎掉入悬崖，三人同时抓住一根藤条，但藤条不能承重三人。市长说：你们谁松手？两随从同时答道：不松！市长无奈道：好吧，既然我是领导，舍己救人是应该的，你们获救后，要好好工作，不辜负组织和人民的期望！好，我的讲话完了！话音刚落，两随从立即鼓掌……&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;14.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女神被高富帅玩腻后无情的抛弃，此时，她想起了吊丝，打电话对吊丝哭诉。吊丝买了鸡蛋和面条，去女神家安慰。吊丝：“我会照顾你一辈子的！”女神：“我换了那么多男朋友，你不嫌弃我吗？”吊丝：“你只是被骗了，我知道你是很纯洁的女孩。”女神感动的哭了起来。吊丝：“不哭了，我下面给你吃。”女神点了点头，蹲下身解开了吊丝裤子的拉链。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;15.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一位女士去做人工绶精的手术。当她脱完衣服躺在床上后，发现医生也开始脱裤子！女士惊叫到：“你要干什么？”医生说：“实在抱歉，瓶装的用完了……”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;16.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2014年度优秀小说评选结果今日接晓，获得特等奖的是短篇小说《夜色》，全篇使用的汉字仅有：来、了、还、不、吗、没以及标点符号。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;夜黑风高，荒郊野岭，小木屋。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男：来了？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女：来了。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男：来？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女：来！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男：来了么？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女：还没！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男：还没来？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女：来了！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;女：还来不？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;男：不来了，来不了了。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;加逗逼美女微信：sm7756&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;，每天都有视频看哦.&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;17.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“我回来了。”他放下包，她坐在沙发上一贯的优雅。“不辛苦的。”他从她明亮的眼睛里看出她要说什么，而她，出生就不能说话。“有你就够了。”他握住她的手，亲了亲她红扑扑的脸蛋。“今晚吃什么呢？泡面吧。”他搂了搂她，心中柔情似水：“乖，我去泡面啦，吃完面就给你充气~”&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;18.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;我女朋友说她前男友比我接吻技巧高多了。我得承认，他确实很棒。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;19.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;洗澡的时候我看出来我绝对不算最大的，但是最悲催的是，我老婆把我们的自拍上传到也漏色网站上的时候，他们居然把录像归类到女同那一类。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;20.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一个男生居然长了三个蛋蛋！但是他不知道自己是不是正常。因为不好意思问同学，于是他决定问哥哥。第二天早上吃饭的时候，他问哥哥：“哥，要是我们两个加起来长了五个蛋蛋，会不会怪阿？”他哥哥听后大惊失色，问其：“你难道长了四个？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;21.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;小龙女被尹志平XXOO后没有怀孕的真相终于被解开了！温95版神雕侠侣，第八集三分五十秒，小龙女被尹志平那啥那啥的时候，尹志平把小龙女的裙子掀上去之后，镜头却切给了旁边的介朵弱弱的野菊花……菊花~~~&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;22.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;上高中，一次偷偷把同学手机里我的号码换成了爸爸，上课时发短信给他：孩子，赶紧回来吧，咱家中了1000万，别上学了！同学看了以后直接往外撒腿就跑，班主任问他干嘛去。他头也不回的地说：去你妈逼，要你管那么多！ 一会又回来了，班主任：滚。这货默默地在外面站了一下午！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;23.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;昨天我一个朋友出院了，不小心被割了皮包，丢了三千块钱，他女朋友臭骂他：“都出院了还靠不住，还丢了钱，真是多此一举！”注：凡是把“皮包”看成了“包皮”的必须评论！ 拥有邪恶的思想的家伙们！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;24.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一天，同事小张问个女同事，你知道胡萝卜可以干什么吗？女：不知道，然后又问：你知道黄瓜可以干什么吗？女：不知道啊。又问：那茄子呢？女：还是不知道。男的无奈说：那馒头呢！女：那个也可以，……&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;br /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#00B0F0;&quot;&gt;25.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;span style=&quot;color:#3F3F3F;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;晶晶和彤彤一起去公共浴室。彤彤刚脱下牛仔裤，晶晶上去一拍彤彤屁股，说，哟，你还和老公穿情侣内裤！……全场安静…… -_-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;div&gt;\r\n					&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n				&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','','1414378960','1414378960','180','257e21c8a9e1be8c','✅姐夫真小气，香蕉都长毛了还藏着','','140','0','0','0',NULL,'1','1','0','1','','');");
E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('141','6','1457963911','知识','1','你的女人，你心疼了吗？','11','生活小常识','http://wx.eake.cn/uploads/2/257e21c8a9e1be8c/d/d/9/6/thumb_544f039f5cec7.jpg','1','&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#E36C09;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#E36C09;&quot;&gt;在很久很久以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;&quot;&gt;前有一群人关注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;了我，然后TA们过上了幸福快乐的生活！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;mid=201415213&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚生活&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;默剧，谈嘻哈生活，说不能说的秘密，发别人不敢发的内容，我们无法自控，还有不敢说的么？每日新鲜、时尚、搞笑、情趣信息，猛点关注，快乐随行，&lt;/span&gt;我们&lt;span&gt;做最出色的自传媒。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#E36C09;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;background-color:#C3D69B;color:#3E3E3E;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;【更多你喜欢的】&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;点击标题上面蓝色字“&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYyNDU3MA==&amp;mid=201415213&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b22d138667085247c432f403f46815c5#rd&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;杰诚生活&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;”关注&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:2em;color:#0070C0;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; \r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7OyHMPuXcPfbzcDILHzCUQ38TdgLoicFdYEs2y1NCtJQJeVKgiaicyqE76HqLo16jD1BibAiabWyxm63Bsy5nMMaHOw/0&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#A5A5A5;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;tn-Powered-by-XIUMI&quot; style=&quot;color:#444444;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-decoration:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;安宁杰诚家政服务有限公司&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;联系电话：0871-68681294&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;h2 class=&quot;rich_media_title&quot; id=&quot;activity-name&quot; style=&quot;font-size:20px;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;\r\n		你的女人，你心疼了吗？\r\n	&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=&quot;page-content&quot; style=&quot;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;div id=&quot;img-content&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_content&quot; id=&quot;js_content&quot; style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					　1、如果你的女人在你面前哭了，无论什么原因，请抱紧她，再反抗也要抱紧，趴在桌子上永远没有在你怀里安心;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGOgk2YPMtxSv5tybjNFMZOrVcDHrQGj5X70ysYqy0vYKhUlZjQv6DLw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　2、如果你的女人和你赌气不理你，不要也学她，这正是考验你们的时候，“脸皮厚”的精神此时不发扬又更待何时;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGvJu4s4OsibWbIkPELkaJVTic29S6vUic9MFVzaYL0vdY2yUIiamR76nT9A/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　3、如果你的女人不听你的话，转身走了，一定要追上她，若真的还爱着，丢下她一个人你又如何放心呢;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGazc6picqcejsfGXcty3q5lucdwyOGb1lNibvsKvsZPh3NSjh9RbKNVnQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　4、如果你的女人说“你走吧，我不想理你了”，千万不要相信，女人最是口是心非，其实那是她最需要你的时候;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBG0SwErwoD8z715Jwo0rYgEBe5nDiatTT042YuH2NQeso1sI2HfZGiaubA/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　5、如果你的女人生气了，说心情不好不想吃饭，千万不要问她想干吗想吃什么，她一定说什么都不要，买好你记忆里她最爱吃的东西(最好是有包装的，这样等她心情好了再吃也不会冷)，但一定不要以自己也不吃来威胁她;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGxoqhrwOhvhwRMWKK9iafJRS4UOOO9K6Oln0kkWu8HTokykMrbyIwSWw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　6、如果你的女人对你们说狠话，请保持三秒钟不说话，然后搂过她的肩，笑笑说：“老婆，你讲话的声音真可爱!”\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGSnsmw0HSK4VkKGJYswhGbeUhJpdfLTnChdKPX5Xyt3d97ASSkgDBuQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;　　&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　7、珍惜你们的女人，不要把她们想的坏想的复杂，女人要的永远最简单!\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGdv08JVognC4aAZOEJqy8mn4VW9CK7KThU3BmUHGP4hUlDeLTicSEdVw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　8、她跟你吵架时不一定就是真有事，而是想撒娇没找对途径，错误的以为这样你就会注意到她;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGq9H2A3yctF3slfaAtjyMmeREwV2rcVevGC4xkWhGXibRNQibPicvInOAg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　9、吵完架不要给她时间冷静，实际上她一点也不需要冷静，她需要你跟她说话哄哄她;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGPXfWJWTp2iaxwdgMpXX3eq6uTKN1MKVhB3b63qsD6xFp63libVMfibDEQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　10、她想哭时先不要问原因，而是在任何时候任何状态下，都先给她一个肩膀让她有依靠;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGoibeibt3Of7e1RZ8iclCZ6edkiaRszLqAYtrUIRRenCdZbGqicMW8CWhy2g/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　11、她梦想一些不切合实际的浪漫时，不要粗暴地打断她，如果连梦想也枯萎的女人更可怕;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGqE7YHo7lDro28reo9CKibxAMFEL87Tq0QkvIlrYuRKlaRCxt9jTzMrg/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　12、大多数时候她都是动态的，你也千万别总是静态，相处时你们更需要互动，哪怕是争执不休;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBG0x1icERpxbnLsPR2o8l3Jibk267CjFibkf6iadh2XgLPhl6pCVSbAhoYGw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　13、女人都是水做的，所以情愿热着她也别冷着她，不然一过了零度她就会结成了冰，最终冻着你;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGhZFUddFicQMXN74GLHxiaGnlyJUvYyE0A4PJVHN9yPTXAwbqFFC3eQ9g/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　14、当她吃醋的时候可不是好玩的，最有效的办法还是让她无醋可吃，要不在醋缸里淹死的可是你;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGEmI4sqkbaUgTHXXbwFpTn4cz3OUk16TFF38pib9uMDPBzIAzf4iaZROQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　15、女人的眼泪并不都是珍珠，但你一定每次都把它们当成珍珠，这样她才会变得连哭都很吝啬;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGgjUexWOrakNu8q68auCC8HXJD9syQP30bjzrzgIuHIIuxkK049OSjQ/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　16、女人都是感性的，所以常会做出一些你认为弱智的事情，也正因为如此，她才需要你的提醒与呵护;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGjic6aG0dx4QCLImgJbk8gDyBLhYIFQxuFmib8cO3RJef4iaPVqd0sS7zw/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　17、她骂你的时候是因为爱你，她打你的时候也是因为爱你，这一点上和男人的表现刚好完全相反;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGRqhOxZlvvzujozC5Yib3ChkfeR3AqdgK22YfYSrMDr6r8pbhKySCq0Q/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n　　18、温柔的女人也会有脾气，坚强的女人也会有脆弱，独立的女人也会有固执，你选择了她就请承担、宽容她的一切!\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Cyr1Xm7ZUQF0ADD2OnyzzZkSmicxe9VBGl0ia3tpicrVQbllETibR5I9fxkicHyevmReNnwSBMiaDWkqLA1OLajicFy0g/640?tp=webp&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n				&lt;p&gt;\r\n					&lt;strong&gt;✄------------------------------------&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n				&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;','','1414464521','1414464521','339','257e21c8a9e1be8c','你的女人，你心疼了吗？','','141','0','0','0',NULL,'1','1','0','1','','');");
